<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <br>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "graham.jpg", width: 250, alt: "profile image", class: 'img-thumbnail' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div
              class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
              role="progressbar"
              aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilised %>"
              aria-valuemax="100"
              style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilised %>%"
              ></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h2>Full Stack Ruby on Rails Developer</h2>
        <p>Recent graduate of Le Wagon Lisbon (Batch #97) - a 9-week intensive coding bootcamp (see link below) - seeking junior full stack, back-end or front-end developer roles in order to build on the skills acquired. Previous to this, I have gained extensive experience as a presentation graphics specialist in the investment banking and management consulting sectors.</p>
        <button
        class="btn btn-primary"
        type="button"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#jobHistory"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controler="jobHistory"
        >
        Job History
      </button>

      <button
      class="btn btn-primary"
      type="button"
      data-toggle="collapse"
      data-target="#education"
      aria-expanded="false"
      aria-controler="education"
      >
      Education
    </button>
  </p>

  <p>
    <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
      <div class="card card-block">
        Job 1
      </div>
      <div class="card card-block">
        Job 2
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="collapse" id="education">
      <div class="card card-block">
        School 1
      </div>
      <div class="card card-block">
        School 2
      </div>
      <div class="card card-block">
        School 3
      </div>
    </div>
  </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
